{
  "id": "pixelbloodpe",
  "name": "PixelBloodPE",
  "author": "ecstsylove",
  "description": "Features",
  "readme_markdown": "<h2><a id=\"user-content-features\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#features\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Customizable blood particle effects.</li>\n<li>Realistic particle spawning based on entity hit positions.</li>\n<li>Configurable options to enable/disable blood effects.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-configuration\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#configuration\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Configuration</h2>\n<p>The configuration file <code>config.yml</code> can be found in the <code>plugin_data/PixelBlood</code> directory. It contains the following options:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-yaml\"><pre><span class=\"pl-c\"><span class=\"pl-c\">#</span> Enables or disables the blood effects</span>\n<span class=\"pl-ent\">blood-enabled</span>: <span class=\"pl-c1\">true</span>\n\n<span class=\"pl-c\"><span class=\"pl-c\">#</span> The particle name to be used for blood effects</span>\n<span class=\"pl-ent\">blood-particle</span>: <span class=\"pl-s\">minecraft:redstone_ore_dust_particle</span></pre></div>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-icon\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#icon\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Icon</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flaticon.com/free-icons/blood\" title=\"blood icons\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blood icons created by srip - Flaticon</a></p>",
